description: Ah, monday again... I was tired after the weekend and really needed some entertainment. So guess what i did!? As I was wandering through busy streets of Prague I´ve found myself a young, scared and a bit nervous guy. He was even shy to talk to me about his girlfriend. But once again, as the majority of youngsters in Prague, he was having some money issues.I started to pick on him about his looks and tiny body which made him even more nervous but to me it was like an aphrodisiac. As soon as I got him into the bushes I couldn´t hold myself any longer. I was a predator and he was a tiny little rabbit!! As he was afraid and humiliated, his cute little body started to shake and that view gave me a real hard on.
title: Czech Hunter 137
